{"tid":391022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校園港獨橫額 盧偉聰稱港獨違反基本法 如違反香港法律警方會嚴正執法","createTime":"2017-09-07T13:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T13:18:02.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"453863304a8ce6ace3e4b419871b95254fb527bf","tid":391022,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"回應大學校園港獨橫額 盧偉聰稱如違法警方會嚴正執法<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰出席觀塘區議會會議時被問到，對於社會出現所謂「違法達義」的行為，及中大校園出現港獨的橫額，警方會如何處理。<span style=\"color: red;\">他說，港獨違反基本法，如有人進行違反香港法律的行為，警方會嚴正執法。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E6%A9%AB%E9%A1%8D-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0%E7%A8%B1%E5%A6%82%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%83%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-085706162.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%25A1%258D-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%2581%25B0%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595-085706162.html&d=5wIftwkErFWQMYrS7QDuyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d86026b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E6%A9%AB%E9%A1%8D-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0%E7%A8%B1%E5%A6%82%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%83%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-085706162.html</a>"},{"pid":"4345606af82858b2d7e488b44679535b9dacf2c3","tid":391022,"uid":57705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e53f8095e175cad04d1bb30b6f93b6e089018a59","tid":391022,"uid":12021,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a